ss runs even when feature not configured |\n| Merged file existence checks | **LOW-MEDIUM** | Extra filesystem ops; minor regression only |\n| Redundant AbsPath calls with errors | **LOW** | Only impacts error paths |\n| Repository handle duplication | **LOW** | Affects only checkpoint fetch path |\n\n**Most critical fix:** Simplify `mergeJSON()` to avoid N+1 parsing, and move `getRemoteURL()` inside the config check in `resolvePushSettings()`.</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>66587</total_tokens><tool_uses>14</tool_uses><duration_ms>36411</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>\nFull transcript available at: /private/tmp/claude-501/-Users-soph-Work-entire-devenv-cli/tasks/a488557b64fe27a24.output\n\n---\n\ncan you now review if it's worth adding more tests\n\n---\n\nlet's add"